Hashrate — is the power of equipment. The higher this figure, the more the miner produces coins.
Power — is the energy consumption of equipment per hour. The cost of maintenance depends on the amount of energy spent.
Revenue 24h — approximate profitability. Changing this value depends on the Difficulty of the network of the block.
